  "prompt": "Top 10 website makers?",
  "response": "There are several popular website builders that are widely considered to be among the best for creating websites. Here's a list of ten highly regarded website makers as of recent years:\n\n1. **Wix** - Known for its intuitive drag-and-drop interface and extensive range of templates and features.\n2. **Squarespace** - Offers beautifully designed templates and a user-friendly builder ideal for creatives.\n3. **WordPress.com** - Provides powerful blogging capabilities and extensive customization options.\n4. **Shopify** - Focused on e-commerce with comprehensive tools for setting up an online store.\n5. **Weebly** - Simple and easy to use with a straightforward drag-and-drop interface.\n6. **GoDaddy Website Builder** - Integrates well with GoDaddy's hosting services, providing an easy-to-use platform.\n7. **Webflow** - Geared towards designers and developers, offering robust customization without coding.\n8. **Jimdo** - Simplifies website building with AI-driven design suggestions and ease of use.\n9. **Site123** - Known for its simplicity and efficiency in creating basic websites quickly.\n10. **Duda** - Offers responsive designs and customization options aimed at small businesses.\n\nThese platforms cater to a variety of needs, from simple personal blogs to complex e-commerce sites, so the best choice will depend on your specific requirements and level of technical expertise.",
